<title>SEND THE GOSPEL LIGHT</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Salhvak in, Aw Salhvak mengin,
 Gam gamla tak chan inle;
 Tanpa deihum tak min ziekin,
 Hukdamna kim thu tunin.

[V2]
 Salhvak in, Aw Salhvak mengin,
 Tuilien khel tuikuol chanin;
 Thusim maktak chuh hetsak in,
 Hehpih, lungsiet manbei chuh!

[V3]
 2. Zan thim lungkham na a thagau,
 Thi dingte chuh hetsak in;
 Kinin, kinin a niu abei,
 Phat kintak in abei zel.

[V4]
 3. Salhvak in Lalpa'n thu ei piei,
 A thu Thiengtho ngaihtuoh un;
 &quot;A tawp chanin hun umpih ka,
 Ka Chanchin Pha gen un ti'n&quot;.</lyrics>
</song>